        <abstract> 
<p>Discusses Mivart’s reply ["Genesis of species", <hi rend="italic">North Am. Rev.</hi> 114 (1872): 451–68] to CW’s review and to Huxley.</p>  
<p>Asks whether CD knows anyone to whom he could usefully send a copy of his phyllotaxy paper [<hi rend="italic">Mem. Am. Acad. Arts &amp; Sci.</hi> n.s. 9 (1867–73): 379–415].</p> 
